# Global Repo Rules

# Env
**/*.env
**/.env.*
!.env.example

# Ignore all IDE settings
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/

# Ignore Dart local build tools
**/.dart_tool/
**/.ds_entraid_sessions/
**/pubspec.lock
**/tmp/pana_*
**/*.exe
**/*.dll
**/*.pdb
**/dart.bat

# Generated analysis and local release artifacts
**/analysis_outputs/
**/analysis_report.txt
**/error_log.txt
**/info_issues.txt
**/warning_issues.txt
**/pub_outdated.txt
**/summary.txt
**/collaboration.txt
**/full_analysis.txt
**/dev-vs-main-changes.patch

# Build and coverage outputs
**/build/
**/coverage/
**/.pub-cache/

# Node and frontend build outputs
**/node_modules/
**/.nuxt/
**/.output/
**/dist/
**/.vite/
**/.cache/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# Firebase local/deployment state
**/.firebase/
**/.firebaserc
**/firebase-debug.log*

# OS files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
